============================================================================= The schema
describes the message format used for ORCID API requests and responses. The top level
element is orcid-message.
Properties
attribute form default: unqualified
element form default: qualified
Element orcid:orcid-message
Namespace http://www.orcid.org/ns/orcid
Annotations
 
The overall container for all ORCID requests and responses.
Diagram
Properties
content: complex
Model orcid:message-version , (orcid:orcid-profile | orcid:orcid-search-results | orcid:error-desc)
Children orcid:error-desc, orcid:message-version, orcid:orcid-profile, orcid:orcid-search-results
Instance
 
<orcid:orcid-message>
  <orcid:message-version>{1,1}</orcid:message-version>
  <orcid:orcid-profile type="user">{1,1}</orcid:orcid-profile>
  <orcid:orcid-search-results>{1,1}</orcid:orcid-search-results>
  <orcid:error-desc>{1,1}</orcid:error-desc>
</orcid:orcid-message>
Source
 
<xs:element name="orcid-message">
  <xs:annotation>
    <xs:documentation>The overall container for all ORCID requests and responses.</xs:documentation>
  </xs:annotation>
  <xs:complexType>
    <xs:sequence>
      <xs:element ref="orcid:message-version"/>
      <xs:choice>
        <xs:element ref="orcid:orcid-profile"/>
        <xs:element ref="orcid:orcid-search-results"/>
        <xs:element ref="orcid:error-desc"/>
      </xs:choice>
    </xs:sequence>
  </xs:complexType>
</xs:element>

Element orcid:creation-method
Namespace http://www.orcid.org/ns/orcid
Annotations
 
The method used to create the profile.
Diagram
Type restriction of xs:string
Properties
content: simple
Facets
enumeration API 
The profile was created using the Tier 2 API.
enumeration manual 
The profile was created manually using the ORCID web user
interface.
Used by
Element orcid:orcid-history
Source
 
<xs:element name="creation-method">
  <xs:annotation>
    <xs:documentation>The method used to create the profile.</xs:documentation>
  </xs:annotation>
  <xs:simpleType>
    <xs:restriction base="xs:string">
      <xs:enumeration value="API">
        <xs:annotation>
          <xs:documentation>The profile was created using the Tier 2 API.</xs:documentation>
        </xs:annotation>
      </xs:enumeration>
      <xs:enumeration value="manual">
        <xs:annotation>
          <xs:documentation>The profile was created manually using the ORCID web user interface.</xs:documentation>
        </xs:annotation>
      </xs:enumeration>
    </xs:restriction>
  </xs:simpleType>
</xs:element>
